# The `R600ControlFlowFinalizer.cpp` File Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

This pass compute turns all control flow pseudo instructions into native one computing their address on the fly; it also sets STACK&#95;SIZE info. <a href="#details">More...</a>
